a:r.a:t: An overview of how PwC manages the delivery, from discover through to application training
Our approach focuses on the involvement and alignment of client stakeholders, through:
Involve to Enhance + Transform new teams
Involve to Train Users and Admins
Engaging concerned stakeholders early and continuously, providing genuine opportunities for two-way communication
Seeking knowledge and insights from those most impacted to help shape the solution
Developing, testing and iterating the change activities with all concerned stakeholders followed by training.
Seeking change readiness insights covering concerned stakeholders to create targeted change management activities
